The paper discusses the evaluation of transformer-based models in natural language understanding tasks, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also discusses the use of large amounts of data and pre-training, which is a common theme in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
